b)	Send the LGU GAD Focal Point System (GFPS) to attend seminars and trainings related to GAD to update their knowledge and build their competencies in the execution of GAD related programs and activities; 

c)	Require the LGU GFPS to conduct HGDG test in evaluating the agency’s PPAs gender sensitivity and responsiveness for client focused activities and GMEF for organization focused activities;

