f)	Maximize the utilization of the GAD funds through the implementation of GAD-related programs and projects in order to attain GAD objectives; and

g)	Justify in writing the utilization of GAD fund in four (4) identified GAD activities as above-mentioned where actual expenditures do not proportionately correspond to the expected output as reflected in the GPB.

